{"tid":950021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"田北辰：條鋼筋係無扭到而唔係剪咗","createTime":"2018-12-21T08:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T06:44:01.000Z","uid":75969,"like":97,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"64a927191eb1ad216a486cc8d7add6a6dd162e83","tid":950021,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181221/s00001/1c41eb19cd7953ab0de2b01cf8e5c3d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181221%2Fs00001%2F1c41eb19cd7953ab0de2b01cf8e5c3d0.jpg&h=196fb538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局證實，港鐵檢查沙中線紅磡站東西走廊B區月台層板工程時，再發現有兩支鋼筋螺絲帽不合格。立法會議員、實政圓桌田北辰認為，如最終在整體檢查的192個鋼筋或螺絲帽中，有兩成鋼筋或螺絲帽接駁不合格，將支持紅磡站擴建月台拆卸重建，「挽回信心危機」。<br />\n<br />\n運房局今日再公布的兩支鋼筋絞牙，僅分別扭入31.61及6.22毫米，其中一支鋼筋絞牙外露8至9個扭紋。田北辰指，反映禮頓及港鐵監工「不知所謂」，「無點扭入都畀佢過到骨」，唯一「不幸中之大幸」，是「條鋼筋係無扭到而唔係剪咗」。<br />\n<br />\n曾任九鐵公司主席的田北辰表示，他最近與九鐵舊同事及多名土木工程專家和承建商等，商討紅磡站事件。他引述有專家最樂觀估計，整體檢查結果如有四成不合格，料仍可加固；但有較保守的專家則指，如超出兩成不合格，已需拆卸重建。<br />\n<br />\n田北辰指，他個人認為事件已超出安全結構問題，社會開始對工程有信心危機，他認同較保守說法，即超出兩成不合格，便需拆掉重建，如此亦可「做到殺雞儆猴，以免日後有承建商有樣學樣，以為四成接駁唔合格，只要加固都過到骨」。<br />\n<br />\n根據港鐵公布鑿石屎檢查方案，將鑿開東西及南北走廊月台層板共80個位置，料至少可以檢查192個鋼筋或螺絲帽，其中24個定點位置每個會開鑿25厘米和深10厘米，推斷每處可見到1個螺絲帽接駁位，即合共約可檢測至少24個螺絲帽；另東西及南北走廊則會「隨機抽樣」合共56個位置，料能檢測至少168個螺絲帽接駁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181221/s00001/1545376661753/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181221%2Fs00001%2F1545376661753%2F&d=KMFAk3JdVptrirVU0BTG%2B8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=8bdf8148\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20181221%2Fs00001%2F1545376661753%2F&h=5b4304b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20181221/s00001/1545376661753/</a>"},{"pid":"40a457a57fd72ae8bb3dfad8b729817683a3f1a2","tid":950021,"uid":5077,"like":558,"dislike":0,"score":558,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:11:59.000Z","msg":"不幸中資大幸"},{"pid":"6ce5213b1470f98c270196b2ff9dc928f2c9c222","tid":950021,"uid":49216,"like":376,"dislike":0,"score":376,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"某某工程師「用手扭都扭到，點會無扭」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed3cbfff89a6fcadb614702efa966bb65d225f0","tid":950021,"uid":41818,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"狗鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c3ff44112a5f9e9a752a3298bf786cc13bdcaa6","tid":950021,"uid":119906,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"條友係咪冇腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9545b60dc1e7f2cefff8abdd823051edf90898d","tid":950021,"uid":7369,"like":112,"dislike":5,"score":107,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"哦, 咁鑿開晒d石屎再扭番晒咪得囉................<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4c4860d58d2b00db1873b29debd0cec90440d2","tid":950021,"uid":6799,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"都係唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7264bb4c2de1d5bcb14711dffa70d17d83bf443b","tid":950021,"uid":4285,"like":189,"dislike":2,"score":187,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"無扭到係仲撚衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n野都唔扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab33331c6440754776f61fa72f2f7d16bb014dad","tid":950021,"uid":191926,"like":161,"dislike":0,"score":161,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T0